flowchart LR
    MEMBER[Community member or participant]
    SURFACE[Post / page / page block / community / event / upload / message]
    ACTIONS[Shared content-actions menu]
    FORM[Contextual report form]
    REPORT[BetterTogether::Report]
    CASE[Safety case]
    REVIEWER[Safety reviewer]
    QUEUE[Review queue and held-content states]
    DECISION[Decision and participant-visible notes]
    FOLLOWUP[Reporter follow-up or appeal note]
    GOV[Governance, accessibility, and product review]
    AUDIT[PublicActivity audit seam]
    FUTURE[Future revision-history work]

    MEMBER --> SURFACE
    SURFACE --> ACTIONS
    ACTIONS --> FORM
    SURFACE -->|block wrapper preserves host extras| ACTIONS
    FORM --> REPORT
    REPORT --> CASE
    CASE --> QUEUE
    REVIEWER --> QUEUE
    QUEUE --> DECISION
    DECISION --> FOLLOWUP
    FOLLOWUP --> CASE

    ACTIONS --> GOV
    QUEUE --> GOV
    DECISION --> GOV
    CASE --> AUDIT
    AUDIT --> FUTURE

    classDef participant fill:#e3f2fd
    classDef workflow fill:#fff3e0
    classDef review fill:#ffebee
    classDef governance fill:#e8f5e8

    class MEMBER,SURFACE,ACTIONS,FORM,FOLLOWUP participant
    class REPORT,CASE,AUDIT workflow
    class REVIEWER,QUEUE,DECISION review
    class GOV,FUTURE governance
